quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  84,1,Igihe ikirere kizasandara (ku munsi w’imperuka)
  84,2,Nuko kikumvira (itegeko rya) Nyagasani wacyo kandi ibyo birakwiye (ko kimwumvira)
  84,3,N’igihe isi izaringanizwa
  84,4,"Maze igasohora ibiyirimo (abapfuye), igasigarira aho"
  84,5,Nuko ikumvira (itegeko rya) Nyagasani wayo kandi ibyo birakwiye (ko imwumvira)
  84,6,"Yewe muntu! Mu by’ukuri, ukorana umuhate imirimo yawe ugana kwa Nyagasani wawe, kandi muzahura (ku munsi w’imperuka)"
  84,7,"Bityo, uzahabwa igitabo cye (cy’ibikorwa bye) mu kuboko kw’iburyo"
  84,8,Azabarurirwa mu buryo bworoshye
  84,9,"Kandi azasubira mu bantu be (umuryango we wakoze neza ku isi, ndetse n’abagore azagororerwa bo mu ijuru) yishimye"
  84,10,"Naho uzahabwa igitabo cye (cy’ibikorwa bye, akacyakirira) inyuma y’umugongo"
  84,11,Azisabira kurimbuka
  84,12,Kandi azinjira mu muriro ugurumana
  84,13,"Mu by’ukuri, (mu buzima bwo ku isi) yabagaho mu muryango we mu bwirasi"
  84,14,"Mu by’ukuri, yibwiraga ko atazagaruka (kwa Nyagasani we)"
  84,15,"Nyamara si byo! Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani we yabaga amubona neza"
  84,16,"Bityo, ndahiriye ku gicu gitukura cy’izuba rirenga"
  84,17,No ku ijoro n’ibyo ritwikira (byose)
  84,18,No ku kwezi igihe kuzuye
  84,19,Ko rwose muzanyura mu byiciro bitandukanye (mu buzima bwa hano ku isi no ku munsi w’imperuka)
  84,20,"Ese babaye bate, kuki batemera"
  84,21,Ndetse n’iyo basomewe Qur’an ntibajya bubama
  84,22,Ahubwo abahakanye bahinyura (Intumwa Muhamadi n’inyigisho zayo)
  84,23,Kandi Allah azi neza ibyo bahisha (mu mitima yabo)
  84,24,"Bityo, bagezeho inkuru y’ibihano bibaza"
  84,25,"Uretse abemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, bazagororerwa ibihembo bidashira (Ijuru)"
  85,1,Ndahiriye ku kirere gifite inyenyeri nini nyinshi
  85,2,No ku munsi w’isezerano (umunsi w’imperuka)
  85,3,No ku munsi w’ubuhamya (umunsi wa Idjuma) ndetse n’umunsi w’ikoraniro (umunsi wa Arafat)
  85,4,Abantu bacukuriye abemeramana imyobo (yo kubatwikiramo) baravumwe
  85,5,Ubwo bacanaga umuriro ugurumana
  85,6,Ubwo bari bawicaye impande
  85,7,Kandi babaga bashungereye ibyo bakoreraga abemeramana (babatwika)
  85,8,"Kandi nta kindi babahoraga usibye kuba baremeye Allah, Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Ushimwa cyane"
  85,9,Ufite ubwami bw’ibirere n’isi! Kandi Allah ni Umuhamya wa buri kintu
  85,10,"Mu by’ukuri, abatoteje abemeramana n’abemeramanakazi (babakorera iyicarubozo), nyuma ntibicuze (kuri Allah), bazahanishwa ibihano by’umuriro wa Jahanamu, banahanishwe ibihano bitwika"
  85,11,"Mu by’ukuri, abemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, bazagororerwa ubusitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru). Iyo ni yo ntsinzi ihebuje"
  85,12,"Mu by’ukuri, ibihano bya Nyagasani wawe (yewe Muhamadi) birakaze"
  85,13,"Mu by’ukuri, ni we waremye (ibiremwa bitari biriho) kandi ni na we uzabigarura (ku munsi w’imperuka)"
  85,14,"Kandi ni we Munyembabazi uhebuje, Umukunzi (w’abemeramana)"
  85,15,Ny’ir’intebe y’icyubahiro
  85,16,Ukora ibyo ashatse
  85,17,Ese wamenye inkuru z’ingabo
  85,18,Za Farawo n’iz’aba Thamudu
  85,19,Ahubwo abahakanye (bakomeje) guhinyura (ukuri)
  85,20,Kandi Allah azi neza ibikorwa byabo byose (kandi azabibahanira)
  85,21,Ahubwo iyi ni Qur’an yubahitse
  85,22,(Yanditse) ku rubaho rurinzwe
  86,1,Ndahiriye ku kirere no ku kimurika nijoro
  86,2,Ni iki cyakumenyesha ikimurika nijoro
  86,3,Ni inyenyeri imurika
  86,4,Nta muntu utagira umugenzuzi (abamalayika bashinzwe kugenzura ibikorwa bya muntu)
  86,5,Ngaho umuntu niyitegereze icyo yaremwemo
  86,6,Yaremwe mu mazi ataruka (intanga)
  86,7,Aturuka hagati y’urutirigongo n’ibituza
  86,8,"Mu by’ukuri, (Allah waremye uwo muntu mu ntanga) afite ubushobozi bwo kumuzura"
  86,9,Umunsi amabanga azahishurwa
  86,10,Icyo gihe (umuntu) nta mbaraga azaba afite cyangwa ngo agire umutabara
  86,11,Ndahiriye ku kirere gitanga imvura igenda igaruka
  86,12,No ku isi isaduka (kugira ngo ibiti n’ibimera bimere)
  86,13,"Mu by’ukuri, iyi (Qur’an) ni ijambo ritandukanya (ukuri n’ikinyoma)"
  86,14,Kandi ntabwo ari ijambo ridafite umumaro
  86,15,"Mu by’ukuri, (abahinyura ukuri) bacura umugambi mubisha (wo kurwanya ubutumwa bw’ukuri)"
  86,16,Maze nanjye (Allah) nkaburizamo umugambi wabo
  86,17,"Bityo, abo bahakanyi bahe igihe (yewe Muhamadi), ubarindirize gato (bazibonera ibizababaho)"